item.title: MoparScape Vet?
item.dc:creator: @Tico135 Tico
item.description:
@Tico135 wrote:

[quote=“Fr33sc4p3, post:3, topic:114907”]All the CM’s were deleted, and a new rank made called ‘MoparScape Vet’, then only a few Vets were picked.

We know make nominate a person to be voted for.

But the vote goes like this, say 2 people said yes and 1 person said no that would be a tie, but if 3 people said yes and 1 person said no then it would be a yes.
If one person said yes and one said no, then it would be no.
Also asking any of us for nomination will decrease or even spoil your chances.[/quote]

Just a question, lets say you were voted no, and the poll closed. Would someone else again be able to nominate them?

item.title: MoparScape Vet?
item.dc:creator: @tL tL
item.description:
@tL wrote:

All the CM’s were deleted, and a new rank made called ‘MoparScape Vet’, then only a few Vets were picked.

We know make nominate a person to be voted for.

But the vote goes like this, say 2 people said yes and 1 person said no that would be a tie, but if 3 people said yes and 1 person said no then it would be a yes.
If one person said yes and one said no, then it would be no.
Also asking any of us for nomination will decrease or even spoil your chances.
